title: [FSX/P3D] Ultimate Terrain Pack USA/EU version 2.1
description:
Pack contains:

- Ultimate Terrain USA (without Alaska and Canada) v 2.1

- Ultimate Terrain EU v 2.1

Quite simple to install just run the installer. After the first installation there 

will be a small manager install.

This is for FSX, P3Dv1 and P3Dv2x ! 


However with the Estonian Migration Tool you can install it in to P3Dv3 not sure

about P3DV3.1. Just remember to deactivate the migration tool after you add it via

manager.



If you like this software please consider buying it !

Simple Thank you will suffice :)



Chears Dace
